pros:
Great benefits packages including private health care for spouse and very good terms for sickness;
Flexible working with the smart working approach suiting family life;
Remote working and working at home;
Managed by objectives and not presenteeism;
Opportunties to move to other roles within the company;
Very family friendly;
Very supportive of diversity;
